query:
UPDATE telegram_channels 
SET isActive = TRUE 
WHERE channelName IN (
  'INEMA.Automacao', 'INEMA.AGENTES', 'INEMA.N8N', 
  'INEMA.Prompts', 'INEMA.LLMs', 'INEMA.IA', 
  'INEMA.TOOLS', 'INEMA.VIP'
);
